OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772197440
OL,3,CMan charged with possession of
OL,4,Coffensive weapon after mosque incident
OL,6,FA man has been charged following an
OL,7,Fincident at Manchester Central Mosque.
OL,9,FDarren Connor, 55, a white British man
OL,10,Ffrom Stockport, has been charged with
OL,11,Fpossession of an offensive weapon and
OL,12,Fpossession of class B drugs.
OL,14,FIt comes after reports suggested a man
OL,15,Fentered a mosque armed with an axe
OL,16,Fduring Ramadan prayers.
OL,18,FGreater Manchester Police confirmed a
OL,19,Fsecond man arrested in connection with
OL,20,Fthe incident will face no further
OL,21,Faction.
